OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773004305
OL,3,CUrgent search for missing skipper
OL,4,Cafter wrecked boat washes up in
OL,5,CCornwall
OL,7,FThere are growing concerns for the
OL,8,Fwelfare of a skipper who is missing
OL,9,Fafter the wreckage of his boat washed
OL,10,Fup on a beach in Cornwall.
OL,12,FDevon and Cornwall Police have issued
OL,13,Fan appeal for help to the community
OL,14,Fafter David Fretwell was reported
OL,15,Fmissing.
OL,17,FThe 75-year-old was reported missing
OL,18,Fafter his boat, Green Goddess, washed
OL,19,Fup in the Hayle area on Friday 6 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
