PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773004305
OL,3,CUrgent search for missing skipper
OL,4,Cafter wrecked boat washes up in
OL,5,CCornwall
OL,7,FThree coastguard vessels, two RNLI
OL,8,Flifeboats and a helicopter were
OL,9,Fscrambled to Mexico Towans beach after
OL,10,FDavid's boat was discovered all
OL,11,Fsmashed up with its contents strewn
OL,12,Facross the sand.
OL,14,FPeople living nearby began to find
OL,15,Fparts of the hull, lifejackets, tins
OL,16,Fof paint coatings, gas canisters,
OL,17,Fpersonal belongings and even a seat,
OL,18,Fstanding upright in the sand. The bulk
OL,19,Fof the debris was strewn around the
OL,20,FMexico Towans area of the beach, close
OL,21,Fto the Beachside Holiday Park.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773004305
OL,3,CUrgent search for missing skipper
OL,4,Cafter wrecked boat washes up in
OL,5,CCornwall
OL,7,FAt the time, a spokesperson for HM
OL,8,FCoastguard said: "A sailing vessel was
OL,9,Freported to HM Coastguard at about
OL,10,F8.05am on Friday, March 6, to have
OL,11,Fbroken up on the shoreline at Hayle
OL,12,Fbeach, with no sign of any person on
OL,13,Fboard.
OL,15,F"Coastguard Rescue Teams from St Ives,
OL,16,FPortreath and Penzance were sent to
OL,17,Fcheck for anyone in distress, as well
OL,18,Fas an HM Coastguard helicopter and two
OL,19,FRNLI lifeboats from St Ives. Devon and
OL,20,FCornwall Police were also informed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773004305
OL,3,CUrgent search for missing skipper
OL,4,Cafter wrecked boat washes up in
OL,5,CCornwall
OL,7,F"Searches did not locate any person in
OL,8,Fdistress. HM Coastguard stood down its
OL,9,Fresponse at about 2.30pm, pending any
OL,10,Fnew information."
OL,12,FDavid is believed to have travelled
OL,13,Falong the north Cornwall coast via
OL,14,Fboat passing Padstow and Newquay
OL,15,Fbefore arriving in the St Ives area on
OL,16,FWednesday (4 March).
OL,18,FDavid is described as a white male, of
OL,19,Fslim build, with short grey hair and
OL,20,Fapproximately 5ft 7in.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
