OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773004305
OL,3,CUrgent search for missing skipper
OL,4,Cafter wrecked boat washes up in
OL,5,CCornwall
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the police force
OL,8,Fsaid: "If you have seen David, or know
OL,9,Fof their whereabouts, please call
OL,10,Fpolice immediately on 999, quoting log
OL,11,Fnumber 247 06/03/26."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
